  "instructions": [
    "Combine pandan leaves, water, and tamarind paste in a blender and blend until smooth.",
    "Heat score-fat in a terracotta dish over medium heat.",
    "Add sliced onion and sauté until translucent.",
    "Add sliced chilies and sauté for another 2 minutes.",
    "Add chopped tomato and sauté for 2 minutes.",
    "Pour in the blended pandan mixture and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in golden syrup, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Continue to simmer for another 5 minutes or until the sauce thickens and forms a glassy-jelly texture.",
    "Serve hot in the terracotta dish."
